# CODEOWNERS - Defines code ownership for PR reviews
# https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositorys-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# When a PR modifies files matching a pattern, the listed owners are
# automatically requested for review. This doesn't "lock" files - it
# ensures the right reviewers see changes.
#
# For Triton Agency: Map bot roles to their service areas.
# The orchestration layer assigns work; CODEOWNERS ensures review routing.

# Default owners (fallback)
* @platform-team

