# Apps (Frontend/UI)
# ============================================
/apps/dashboard/                    @frontend-team
/apps/landing/                      @frontend-team

# ============================================
# Services (Backend)
# ============================================
/services/api/                      @backend-team
/services/auth/                     @backend-team

# ============================================
